NAME
    Dist::Zilla::App::Command::dhmakeperl - use dh-make-perl to generate
    .deb archives from your CPAN package

VERSION
    version 0.001

METHODS
  abstract
  opt_spec
  validate_args
  execute
NOTES
    *   You must have dh-make-perl installed on your system to use this
        command. use sudo apt-get install dh-make-perl to install it on
        debian and ubuntu

SUPPORT
  Bugs / Feature Requests
    Please report any bugs or feature requests through github at
    <https://github.com/shantanubhadoria/dist-zilla-app-command-dhmakeperl/i
    ssues>. You will be notified automatically of any progress on your
    issue.

